/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Отзыв 1: The Facebook group recommended your site! I didn't really believe that it was possible to find someone like that, but I found a nanny in a week! There is a large selection of nannies who are checked by specialists.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Отзыв 2: I found a vacancy for a caregiver on Giupchame and wrote to the employer I was invited to an interview, now I have already started working. It is convenient to look for vacancies near home. I recommend this platform to everyone!
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Отзыв 3: I am personally satisfied with the work of the site. Everything is legal, safe and reliable. I have found an amazing nanny-housekeeper who already works with us. I always recommend this platform to all my friends!
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Рекомендуем раз: We recommend that you place your search ad so that employees can submit their resumes. You may also choose a candidate by yourself in the Search section.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.На основании че: What is the rating based on?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Рейтинг формиру: The rating is formed on the basis of feedback from employers and the completion of the employee's profile.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Как посмотреть: How can  I view employee reviews?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Отзыв публикует: The review is published in the questionnaire at the very bottom. If the Leave Feedback button is displayed, then the employee has no feedback yet. At the same time, the candidate may have personal recommendations.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Как найти работ: How do I find an employee close to my home?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.В разделе Поиск: In the Search section, set the minimum distance in the filters and click the Apply button. The system will show you all the employees who live near you.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Нужно ли оплачи: Do I need to pay for the services of the site?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Для работников: The site is free for employees. You do not need to pay for registration and responses.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Как быстрее най: How to find a job faster?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Рекомендуем мак: We recommend filling out your resume as detailed as possible, actively responding to vacancies (at least 5 responses per day) and promptly responding to messages in Chats.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Обязательно ли: Is it obligatory to upload personal photos and photos of diplomas to the site?
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Рекомендуем заг: We recommend uploading these photos if you are interested in finding a well-deserved job in a short time.
/Views/Home/Index.cshtml.Повышая рейтинг: By increasing your rating, you noticeably stand out among other candidates, increase the trust of employers and receive more job offers.

Все работники размещены на карте города, что позволит вам договориться с
Поиск работы абсолютно бесплатный. Никаких дополнительных платных услуг у нас нет и не будет! С нами вы зарабатываете деньги, а не тратите.

На Помогателе найдется работа с любым графиком: полный рабочий день, вахта с проживанием или подработка на несколько часов в день. Есть и варианты нерегулярной работы, например, на пару недель или разово.
Не тратьте время на долгую дорогу утром на работу и вечером обратно домой, выбирайте вакансии поблизости. Проводите больше времени с родными и друзьями.
